{"tid":2249705,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"視訊粉絲聽到「對不起⋯」真心話　ROSÉ感性大噴淚⋯自己都崩潰","createTime":"2020-10-19T13:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T13:56:13.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"04d521d370c03a80b0849d07599e02bcdec516f6","tid":2249705,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:31:57.000Z","msg":"南韓女團BLACKPINK出道4年，首次推出正規專輯《The Album》，也透過「視訊簽售會」的方式與粉絲在線上面對面交流。近來有粉絲公開與成員ROS&Eacute;視訊的畫面，只見粉絲在對她說出一段話後，讓ROS&Eacute;忍不住落淚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5214/d5214691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5214%2Fd5214691.jpg&h=39b0ef9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK ROS&Eacute;聽到粉絲說「對不起」，露出難過的表情。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n粉絲公開與ROS&Eacute;視訊的畫面，對話中，粉絲說道：「這段時間，一直說希望妳去做什麼做什麼的，也許會讓妳覺得有負擔。覺得很抱歉，妳想做什麼、無論什麼時候，都去做吧，我會一直支持妳的。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5214/d5214694.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5214%2Fd5214694.jpg&h=7150e1f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ROS&Eacute;聽到粉絲說「對不起」和鼓勵的話，忍不住流下眼淚。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n感性的ROS&Eacute;聽到這段話後，一邊搖著手說著：「這沒有什麼需要抱歉的」一邊忍不住偷偷擦眼淚。後來似乎覺得有點不好意思，自嘲的說著：「哎唷這太好笑了啦」但還是繼續擦眼淚。感性的ROS&Eacute;也引起韓網討論，有人稱讚她反應可愛，也有人說：「因為這段話真的很感人。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5214/d5214692.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5214%2Fd5214692.jpg&h=b73fe87e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ROS&Eacute;爆淚連自己都嚇到，邊哭邊笑大崩潰。（圖／翻攝自韓網）"},{"pid":"1cc1ca21f3c00c8b17cfe1dd810dd3101a5cd972","tid":2249705,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:33:02.000Z","msg":"哭𠹌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02fbace2bc81c4c81ced786f5a72d914d3d1a7af","tid":2249705,"uid":219225,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:34:5